        <p>A WinningLife Business Owner (WBO) is expected to operate the business according to the highest standards of
          integrity
          and fair practice in the role as a WBO. Additionally WBO’s should note that failure to comply with the code of
          ethics
          set out in section 2 below, can result in your termination as a WBO.</p>
        <p>This terms and conditions contain all the agreement between the company and the independent WBO.</p>
