      <div>
        <h2>2. CODE OF ETHICS FOR A WINNINGLIFE BUSINESS OWNER (WBO)</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>I will conduct my business in an honest ethical manner at all times.</li>
          <li>I will make no representation about the benefits of membership with the company other than those contained
