          <li>I will motivate and actively work with fellow business owners in my team to help them build their
            WinningLife business. I understand that this support is critical to each WBO’s success.</li>
          <li>I will refrain from exaggerating my personal income or the income potential in general and will stress to
            prospective
            WBO’s, the level of effort and commitment required to succeed in the business.</li>
          <li>I will not make disparaging remarks about other products, services or companies. Likewise, I will not
            willfully
            denigrate the activities or personalities of fellow WBO’s or WinningLife staff or agents.</li>
          <li>I will not make disparaging remarks about other products, services or companies. Likewise, I will not
            willfully
            denigrate the activities or personalities of fellow WBO’s or WinningLife staff or agents.</li>
          <li>I will abide by all of the policies and procedures of WinningLife as included herein, or as may be amended
